  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether folate produced by bacteria that live in
      our colon can be absorbed in human colon using a stable isotope method. This study would lead
      a better understanding of the bioavailability of colonic bacterially-synthesized folate and
      its quantitative contribution to whole body folate homeostasis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
